    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095160/extras/3b31ea974006da55a19ff2a420dfe75f.webp?t=1747593228\" width=600 height=39 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在“Domovoy”游戏中，您将沉浸在乍一看完全普通的公寓中，但您走得越远，IT就越揭示其本质。这款恐怖游戏是第一人称步行模拟器，气氛紧张，探索公寓，找到答案并继续前进。你准备好去见他了吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095160/extras/b2aa998278e05fd0a92407ba21e72c27.poster.avif?t=1747593228\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095160/extras/b2aa998278e05fd0a92407ba21e72c27.webm?t=1747593228\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095160/extras/b2aa998278e05fd0a92407ba21e72c27.mp4?t=1747593228\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095160/extras/50f3f656475cbc54518911f0179e1238.webp?t=1747593228\" width=600 height=39 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >布朗尼不仅是壁炉的守护者，也是复仇之魂。如果被忽视或不尊重，它可能会背叛它的主人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095160/extras/76bd832976b06d7caa15f3d308c030a4.poster.avif?t=1747593228\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095160/extras/76bd832976b06d7caa15f3d308c030a4.webm?t=1747593228\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095160/extras/76bd832976b06d7caa15f3d308c030a4.mp4?t=1747593228\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095160/extras/1c7de0b26f326dbee5ef80c70c6c9ad7.webp?t=1747593228\" width=600 height=39 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >八十年代末苏联的气氛</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >步行模拟器</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >斯拉夫神话</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >逼真的图形</p></li></ul>",
